WEBVTT

00:00.329 --> 00:02.158
Now, I wanna add something to my space.

00:02.236 --> 00:04.871
So, I'm gonna pull up my holographic Start menu,...

00:06.723 --> 00:11.002
...and I'm gonna open up Skype.

00:11.435 --> 00:13.361
I'm the worst at keeping in touch.

00:13.619 --> 00:16.634
So, I'm gonna take the people that matter most to me,...

00:18.673 --> 00:22.364
...and I'm gonna pin them to this wall right here.

00:23.355 --> 00:27.413
That way, every time I walk into this room, I'll see their smiling faces...

00:27.473 --> 00:28.963
...and be inspired to reach out to them.

00:30.516 --> 00:34.249
Then if I look up here on the wall, to my left, I've got a video player.

00:35.109 --> 00:39.345
I simply reach out, air tap, and I'm right in the action.

